* Dido Elizabeth Belle (1761–1804), born into slavery but raised as a free woman by Lord Mansfield, her uncle
* &quot;Belle&quot;, 2013 film

* &quot;La Amistad&quot;, a ship involved in an important slavery related court case in the US

