<text>ROCS &quot;Su Ao (蘇澳; DDG-1802) is a guided-missile destroyer currently in active service of the Republic of China Navy. &quot;Su Ao&quot; was formerly American , which was decommissioned from the United States Navy in 1998. For some time after the ship&#x27;s 30 May 2003 purchase, &quot;Su Ao&quot; was tentatively named Ming Teh&quot; (明德), following the example of &quot;Chi Teh&quot; (紀德), but it was later decided to be named &quot;Su Ao&quot;, after the Su-Ao naval base in eastern Taiwan.</text><links>
